- using dir_tree() function from {fs} package

- Description
Print contents of directories in a tree-like format

- Arguments
-  path:A path to print the tree from
-  recurse: If TRUE recurse fully, if a positive number the number of levels to recurse.
-  max_depth: max number of levels on the folder structure to be displayed
...	
Arguments passed on to dir_ls

> dir_tree(recursive = FALSE, max_depth = 1)
Warning: `recursive` is deprecated, please use `recurse` instead
